The 07 produces a large fan with very soft atomization. It is a great gun for blending metallics. The 07 gun comes standard with our new cup with a twist lock lid. The gun is available with either a 600ml or 1000ml cup. Accuspray offers a variety of needle, nozzle and air cap sizes for the 07 guns to meet your application needs.

Includes:

  • Your Choice of needle size
  • Your Choice of Air Cap size
  • Your Choice of 650 ml. plastic, 1000ml, 600ml, or 200ml Teflon anodized cup
  • Stainless Steel Fluid Passage
